panels.description: I/O wait CPU load ~ time spent (%) waiting for I/O operations to complete

targets.query: SELECT MAX("MAX_iowait_load") AS "MAX", MEAN("MEAN_iowait_load") AS "Mean", MEAN("MEDIAN_iowait_load") AS "Median", MIN("MIN_iowait_load") AS "MIN" FROM "history"."cpu_info" WHERE ${timeFilter} AND "task" =~ /^${Task}$/ AND "serie" =~ /^${Serie}$/ AND "host" =~ /^${Host}$/ GROUP BY time(${__interval})

panels.title: CPU - Wait

panels.description: System CPU load ~ time spent (%) in kernel space (I/Os, device drivers, etc.)

targets.query: SELECT MAX("MAX_system_load") AS "MAX", MEAN("MEAN_system_load") AS "Mean", MEAN("MEDIAN_system_load") AS "Median", MIN("MIN_system_load") AS "MIN" FROM "history"."cpu_info" WHERE ${timeFilter} AND "task" =~ /^${Task}$/ AND "serie" =~ /^${Serie}$/ AND "host" =~ /^${Host}$/ GROUP BY time(${__interval})

panels.title: CPU - System

panels.description: User CPU load ~ time spent (%) in user space (actual computation)

targets.query: SELECT MAX("MAX_user_load") AS "MAX", MEAN("MEAN_user_load") AS "Mean", MEAN("MEDIAN_user_load") AS "Median", MIN("MIN_user_load") AS "MIN" FROM "history"."cpu_info" WHERE ${timeFilter} AND "task" =~ /^${Task}$/ AND "serie" =~ /^${Serie}$/ AND "host" =~ /^${Host}$/ GROUP BY time(${__interval})

panels.title: CPU - User

panels.description: Nice CPU load ~ time spent (%) in (re)niced user space (actual computation)

targets.query: SELECT MAX("MAX_nice_load") AS "MAX", MEAN("MEAN_nice_load") AS "Mean", MEAN("MEDIAN_nice_load") AS "Median", MIN("MIN_nice_load") AS "MIN" FROM "history"."cpu_info" WHERE ${timeFilter} AND "task" =~ /^${Task}$/ AND "serie" =~ /^${Serie}$/ AND "host" =~ /^${Host}$/ GROUP BY time(${__interval})

panels.title: CPU - Nice

targets.query: SELECT MAX("MAX") AS "MAX", MEAN("Mean") AS "Mean", MEAN("Median") AS "Median", MIN("MIN") AS "MIN" FROM (SELECT MAX("MAX_total_bytes")-MIN("MIN_available_bytes") AS "MAX", MAX("MAX_total_bytes")-MEAN("MEAN_available_bytes") AS "Mean", MAX("MAX_total_bytes")-MEAN("MEDIAN_available_bytes") AS "Median", MAX("MAX_total_bytes")-MAX("MAX_available_bytes") AS "MIN" FROM "history"."mem_info" WHERE "task" =~ /^${Task}$/ AND "serie" =~ /^${Serie}$/ AND "host" =~ /^${Host}$/ GROUP BY *) WHERE ${timeFilter} GROUP BY time(${__interval})

panels.description: Memory used, including (reclaimable) buffers and cache

targets.query: SELECT MAX("MAX") AS "MAX", MEAN("Mean") AS "Mean", MEAN("Median") AS "Median", MIN("MIN") AS "MIN" FROM (SELECT MAX("MAX_total_bytes")-MIN("MIN_free_bytes") AS "MAX", MAX("MAX_total_bytes")-MEAN("MEAN_free_bytes") AS "Mean", MAX("MAX_total_bytes")-MEAN("MEDIAN_free_bytes") AS "Median", MAX("MAX_total_bytes")-MAX("MAX_free_bytes") AS "MIN" FROM "history"."mem_info" WHERE "task" =~ /^${Task}$/ AND "serie" =~ /^${Serie}$/ AND "host" =~ /^${Host}$/ GROUP BY *) WHERE ${timeFilter} GROUP BY time(${__interval})

panels.title: Memory - Used

panels.description: Writes time spent waiting for device to complete operations

targets.query: SELECT MAX("MAX_writes_latency_seconds_per_op") AS "MAX", MEAN("MEAN_writes_latency_seconds_per_op") AS "Mean", MEAN("MEDIAN_writes_latency_seconds_per_op") AS "Median", MIN("MIN_writes_latency_seconds_per_op") AS "MIN" FROM "history"."io_disk" WHERE ${timeFilter} AND "task" =~ /^${Task}$/ AND "serie" =~ /^${Serie}$/ AND "host" =~ /^${Host}$/ AND "device" =~ /^${Disk}$/ GROUP BY time(${__interval})

panels.title: Disk - WR:latency

panels.description: Writes bytes, actually written to device

targets.query: SELECT 512*MAX("MAX_writes_sectors_per_second") AS "MAX", 512*MEAN("MEAN_writes_sectors_per_second") AS "Mean", 512*MEAN("MEDIAN_writes_sectors_per_second") AS "Median", 512*MIN("MIN_writes_sectors_per_second") AS "MIN" FROM "history"."io_disk" WHERE ${timeFilter} AND "task" =~ /^${Task}$/ AND "serie" =~ /^${Serie}$/ AND "host" =~ /^${Host}$/ AND "device" =~ /^${Disk}$/ GROUP BY time(${__interval})

targets.query: SELECT MAX("MAX_writes_completed_per_second") AS "MAX", MEAN("MEAN_writes_completed_per_second") AS "Mean", MEAN("MEDIAN_writes_completed_per_second") AS "Median", MIN("MIN_writes_completed_per_second") AS "MIN" FROM "history"."io_disk" WHERE ${timeFilter} AND "task" =~ /^${Task}$/ AND "serie" =~ /^${Serie}$/ AND "host" =~ /^${Host}$/ AND "device" =~ /^${Disk}$/ GROUP BY time(${__interval})

panels.title: Disk - RD:iops

targets.query: SELECT MAX("MAX_tx_bytes_per_second") AS "MAX", MEAN("MEAN_tx_bytes_per_second") AS "Mean", MEAN("MEDIAN_tx_bytes_per_second") AS "Median", MIN("MIN_tx_bytes_per_second") AS "MIN" FROM "history"."net_dev" WHERE ${timeFilter} AND "task" =~ /^${Task}$/ AND "serie" =~ /^${Serie}$/ AND "host" =~ /^${Host}$/ AND "device" =~ /^${IFace}$/ GROUP BY time(${__interval})

list.name: Task
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "history"."cpu_info" WITH KEY = "task"

list.name: Serie
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "history"."cpu_info" WITH KEY = "serie" WHERE "task" =~ /^${Task}$/

list.name: Host
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "history"."cpu_info" WITH KEY = "host" WHERE "task" =~ /^${Task}$/ AND "serie" =~ /^${Serie}$/

list.name: Disk
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "history"."io_disk" WITH KEY = "device" WHERE "task" =~ /^${Task}$/ AND "serie" =~ /^${Serie}$/ AND "host" =~ /^${Host}$/

list.name: IFace
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "history"."net_dev" WITH KEY = "device" WHERE "task" =~ /^${Task}$/ AND "serie" =~ /^${Serie}$/ AND "host" =~ /^${Host}$/
